headline: Dolci Frutta Announces New Non-Alcoholic Collaboration with Baileys® Irish Cream
summary: A decadent new addition to Dolci Frutta's popular hard-shell dessert line, featuring the delicious flavor of Baileys Irish Cream, is hitting shelves just in time for the holidays.
